  "texts": [
    "However, it is necessary to validate that numeric hyperparameters such as temperature have numeric values.",
    "PromptsPrompts are defined as a sequence of snippets.",
    "One snippet is identified as the prefix (suffix) and is prepended (appended) to the rest of the prompt, while the rest form the core of the prompt.A snippet can contain a textual literal, a reference to one of the prompt's parameters or to another asset to be reused (allowing for modular definitions of prompts).",
    "Moreover, a snippet can also include a property about the output (called trait) chosen from a predefined catalog.",
    "Figure 2 presents the traits that are independent of the format of the prompt's output."
  ],
